{"tid":2204332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國政府涉駭客攻擊美機構 美國司法部預告逮捕行動","createTime":"2020-09-16T03:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T03:59:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b84da6b5d698672b09ad4a59589057286d7ee21","tid":2204332,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓15日綜合外電報導）美國司法部今天聲明表示，將宣布數起「與中國政府有牽連的電腦入侵行動相關起訴及逮捕案」。<br />\n<br />\n根據聲明，美國司法部次長羅森（Jeffrey Rosen）、聯邦調查局（FBI）副局長鮑迪希（David Bowdich）等官員將於美國東部夏令時間16日上午11時（台灣時間晚間11時）出席記者會並宣布此事。聲明並未提到其他細節。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，白宮國家安全顧問歐布萊恩（Robert O'Brien）今年8月曾表示，距離11月3日美國總統大選愈來愈近，與中國政府有關的駭客一直鎖定美國選舉基礎設施為行動目標。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府指控中國駭入美國企業、政治人物或政府機關，但中國向來否認。（譯者：曾依璇/核稿：張曉雯）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009160028.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202009160028.aspx&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=8b910ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009160028.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"578602ac8db4981ea393db6a29bdee93d0d0a96b","tid":2204332,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a90d2054ea2605ad272077abd59aff4a168ff9","tid":2204332,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca0129b6fa58065949