trusion campaign tied to the Chinese government,&rdquo; the department said in a statement on Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\nDeputy Attorney General Jeffrey Rosen, FBI Deputy Director David Bowdich and other officials will take part in a news conference at 11 a.m. EDT (1500 GMT) on Wednesday to make the announcement, the statement said.<br />\n<br />\nNo other details were given.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-hack/u-s-to-announce-on-wednesday-charges-in-computer-intrusion-campaigns-related-to-china-idUSKBN2663H0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-hack%2Fu-s-to-announce-on-wednesday-charges-in-computer-intrusion-campaigns-related-to-china-idUSKBN2663H0&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=30dd5bc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-hack%2Fu-s-to-announce-on-wednesday-charges-in-computer-intrusion-campaigns-related-to-china-idUSKBN2663H0&h=b35f6369\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-hack/u-s-to-announce-on-wednesday-charges-in-computer-intrusion-campaigns-related-to-china-idUSKBN2663H0</a>"},{"pid":"e8307c1667135fd96c1d3a8fd51d979d28797dcb","tid":2204332,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}